    "bio": "🌟 About Me 🌟\nI am a passionate and driven individual who thrives on learning and adapting to any situation. My mission is to create impactful, end-to-end products in the domains of productivity, learning, AI, and finance. With a strong foundation in backend development, LLMs, and data engineering, I bring intermediate-level expertise in AI, DevOps, and frontend development, alongside a growing interest in UI/UX and product design.",
